  "Sanction Details" : "SIMULTANEOUS WITH THE FILING OF THE COMPLAINT, GOLDBERG CONSENTED, WITHOUT ADMITTING OR DENYING THE ALLEGATIONS IN THE COMPLAINT, TO THE ENTRY OF A FINAL JUDGMENT: (1) PERMANENTLY ENJOINING HIM FROM VIOLATING SECTION 10(B) OF THE EXCHANGE ACT AND RULE 10B-5 THEREUNDER; (2) ORDERING HIM TO DISGORGE $28,546 IN ILLEGAL PROFITS AND TO PAY PREJUDGMENT INTEREST OF $3,553; AND (3) ORDERING HIM TO PAY A CIVIL PENALTY OF $57,092, WHICH REPRESENTS TWO TIMES THE AMOUNT OF HIS ILLEGAL PROFITS.  "
